Known limitations (intentionally deferred):
  - composio.trigger.disabled is log-only (schema lacks `active` column;
    full mark-inactive + alert flow is a follow-up).
  - emitConnectionExpiredEvent attaches to the globally most-recent open
    run, not workspace-scoped (we don't persist connected_account_id →
    workspace_id mapping locally). Documented in code.
  - Worker doesn't yet inject cloud_runs.inputs into the agent prompt
    (same D.x-deferred gap as D.3).

